description: Get Ready for your outdoor adventure with the exclusive Baby Trend Expedition 2-in-1 Stroller Wagon! Designed with utility, safety and style, the Expedition 2-in-1 Stroller Wagon is for the family that loves outdoor activities and discovery. The super large cargo space with built-in seating and the two 3-point safety harness belt allows kids to explore with safety. Plus, the extra-large ratcheting canopy with UPF 50+ protection and air-flow mosquito netting keeps your little ones away from the harmful sun-rays and rain. Parents will also love the Ultimate Storage Solutions, which includes parent and child trays with 2 cup holders and center consoles, plus 2 additional cup holders outside of the wagon. The Baby Trend Expedition 2-in-1 Stroller Wagon is equipped with easy one button removable 11" rear wheels and durable 8" front wheels for easy maneuverability.
